tep 1: Choose Weather API

Use a reliable weather API to get rain forecasts:

OpenWeatherMap (Free & Easy
)

Endpoint: https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/forecast

Returns 5-day forecast with 3-hour intervals

WeatherAPI (Free Plan
)

Endpoint: /forecast.json

Returns daily/hourly rain forecast

